      • PICT

        @Deprecated
@Removal(version="5.3")
public PICT()
        Deprecated.
        Use HSLFSlideShow.addPicture(byte[], org.apache.poi.sl.usermodel.PictureData.PictureType) or one of its overloads to create new PICT. This API led to detached PICT instances (See Bugzilla 46122) and prevented adding additional functionality.

        bse - Record referencing this picture. Should be attached to the slideshow that this picture is linked to.
